      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Front Seat Frame Removal and Installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If there are components of the SRS airbag system in the vicinity, refer to the work precautions and configuration drawings described for the SRS airbag system before proceeding."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If the side airbags have deployed, replace the seat frame and related parts."
    },
